{"title":"contos 安装 python 3.3","date":"2016-03-29T02:10:37.000Z","author":"Wenbin","link":"contos-安装-python-3-3","comments":true,"categories":["其他"],"updated":"2020-04-15T21:36:20.855Z","content":"<p>查看当前系统中的python版本</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>安装所有的开发工具包</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum groupinstall \"Development tools\"</span><br><span class=\"line\">```shell</span><br><span class=\"line\">yum install zlib-devel bzip2-devel openssl-devel ncurses-devel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>下载、编译和安装Python<br>在官网下载python 3.3版本源码：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget http://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.3.0/Python-3.3.0.tar.bz2</span><br><span class=\"line\">tar -jxv -f Python-3.3.0.tar.bz2</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd Python-3.3.0</span><br><span class=\"line\">./configure</span><br><span class=\"line\">make install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"常用 css lib","link":"常用-css-lib"},"next":{"title":"pm2 入门","link":"pm2-入门"},"plink":"https://wuwb.github.io/contos-安装-python-3-3/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Wenbin","link":"<a href=\"https://wuwb.github.io/contos-安装-python-3-3/\" title=\"contos 安装 python 3.3\">https://wuwb.github.io/contos-安装-python-3-3/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd